00:05:04.722 --> 00:05:06.825
Why is there this discrepancy?

00:05:06.849 --> 00:05:09.563
It seems that we're doing
a comparative evaluation.

00:05:09.587 --> 00:05:11.491
"Compared to the victim,

00:05:11.515 --> 00:05:13.793
nothing really happened to me."

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:16.268
But that's not really the right question.

00:05:16.292 --> 00:05:17.990
And support shouldn't be invisible

00:05:18.014 --> 00:05:20.442
just because you're less affected.

00:05:20.760 --> 00:05:22.045
Because we're all affected

00:05:22.069 --> 00:05:24.759
and we should all
be supporting each other.

